"本单位可以自动恢复生命值，因此可以治疗自己受到的伤害，仿佛一直处在村庄里一"
"样。"

#: data/core/special-notes.cfg:17
msgid ""
" The steadiness of this unit reduces damage from some attacks, but only "
"while defending."
